{"tid":59954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李卓人評飲食業僱主「食到最盡最賤」","createTime":"2016-12-30T05:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T07:52:28.000Z","uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2ec2630de9984fb99cc7ceda31ba27aeb9768e","tid":59954,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"一名在元朗酒樓任職13年的點心師傅被僱主解僱，原應獲逾30萬長期服務金及累積假期等賠償，但僱主僅付7天代通知金約5,000元，入稟勞資審裁處也追討不果，因該僱主一直只以短期合約聘用，每18個月便中斷僱員年資一次，不但逃避長期服務金及遣散費，更清走員工年假及斷供強積金，剝削僱員權益。"},{"pid":"55360d672738ae9873bbd8803b1ebbb524578d91","tid":59954,"uid":32370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981b54e92955af8e592462b02a4f8ed188786ed8","tid":59954,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲食業真係狗"},{"pid":"df40d3d5c5d698f9787d8d9c13d2c7ab2a1ee14e","tid":59954,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲食業真係狗</blockquote><br />\n其實唔少行業都狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假自僱咪又一樣"},{"pid":"4f7bf31bbd3145a7225b6213734bd92f63401eeb","tid":59954,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"如果無人肯做垃圾工就唔會有垃圾工"},{"pid":"ec67b7215d6da53fcbf9e04c861b857148732e3c","tid":59954,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"呢種做法都唔係只係飲食業啦。咩行業都係咁.<br />\n政府工都行contract制啦.<br />\n<br />\n惡性循環"},{"pid":"12ae1be26487d77397166e5a7252f1c0f8482dd9","tid":59954,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep